<i>noun</i>: 비료 [비ː료], 거름 [거름] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>비료 [비ː료]</dt><br>
<dd>fertilizer</dd><br>
<dd>농사를 지을 때 땅을 기름지게 만들어 식물이 잘 자라게 하려고 뿌리는 물질.</dd><br>
<dd>A substance for farming that one spreads over soil to make land fertile, and therefore enable crops to grow well.</dd><br>
<dt>거름 [거름]</dt><br>
<dd>1. manure; fertilizer</dd><br>
<dd>식물이 잘 자라도록 땅에 뿌리거나 섞는 물질.</dd><br>
<dd>Substance scattered over or mixed into the soil for plants to grow well.</dd><br>
<dd>2. aid; help</dd><br>
<dd>무엇이 잘 되게 돕는 밑바탕.</dd><br>
<dd>Something helping a person or an event to succeed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>